    "brainstorm_custom_instructions": "Ongerako kanaka focus ubuso canke requirements kuri brainstorm.",
    "persona_panel": "AI Persona ibiganiro urubaho - engage muri authentic conversations hamwe na historical figures, scientists, literary umuntu, canke gakondo personas. Uses co hejuru AI ku simulate period-accurate speech imiterere, knowledge, na perspectives. Perfect kuri primary imvo analysis, perspective-taking, na empathy-building exercises. imfashanyo vyinshi response uburyo: Muri-umuntu (fully birimo), Educational (hamwe na kwiga scaffolds), canke Mixed (balanced approach).",
    "persona_card": "AI persona ready kuri conversation. buri ikarata irerekana umuntu's name, time period, na expertise ubuso. Kanda ku tangura interview - AI will respond authentically bishingiye kuri their historical context, beliefs, na knowledge. Koresha personas kuri primary imvo analysis, perspective-taking exercises, canke creative kwandika inspiration.",
    "persona_generate_button": "Kora AI personas automatically kuva cawe imvo ibirimwo. sisitemu analyzes cawe inyandiko ku kumenya key figures, historical periods, canke umuntu archetypes na irema authentic conversational partners. Vyakozwe personas shiramwo accurate biographical ibisigura, period-appropriate amajambo, na contextual knowledge limitations (they won't know ku byerekeye events after their time).",
    "persona_select_button": "Hitamwo iki persona ku begin cawe interview canke conversation. Once vyahisemwo, wewe'll injiza birimo ibiganiro interface aho wewe can ask ikibazo, sesengura their perspective, na earn XP kuri meaningful exchanges. AI responds bishingiye kuri umuntu's historical knowledge, personality, na cultural context.",
    "persona_back_btn": "Return ku persona selection icyuma ku hitamwo different umuntu. cawe current conversation iterambere ni automatically vyabitswe, na wewe can return ku bandanya it later. Iki allows exploring vyinshi perspectives kuri kimwe historical ikiyago.",
    "persona_custom_instructions": "Ongerako kanaka requirements kuri how persona should behave during conversations. akarorero: focus kuri kanaka time period, emphasize certain beliefs canke agaciro, maintain particular speech imiterere, canke limit responses ku historically accurate knowledge. umwigisha can koresha iki ku align personas hamwe na kanaka kwiga objectives.",
    "persona_response_mode": "Hitamwo how persona responds ku rema different kwiga ubuhinga. IN umuntu: Fully birimo historical ijwi hamwe na no uburyorn explanations. EDUCATIONAL: umuntu speaks ariko hariho kwiga scaffolds, amajambo imfashanyo, na context. MIXED: Balanced approach hamwe na authentic ijwi plus occasional clarifications. Hitamwo bishingiye kuri umunyeshure readiness na kwiga intumbero.",
    "persona_free_response": "Type cawe own yugurura-ended response instead ca selecting kuva pre-written amahitamwo. Free response uburyo promotes creative expression, critical thinking, na authentic dialogue ubuhinga. Responses ni analyzed kuri historical ukuri, empathy, na ubujambere ca inquiry. Higher-quality ikibazo earn vyinshi XP.",
    "persona_hints_toggle": "Erekana canke nyegeza response suggestions na conversation impanuro. igihe enabled, sisitemu provides scaffolded ikibazo starters, historical conikiganiro amabwiriza, na engagement suggestions. Ubufashaful kuri umunyeshure gisha ku historical inquiry canke those needing imfashanyo hamwe na yugurura-ended ikibazoing. umwigisha can hagarika impanuro kuri vyinshi co hejuru igenzura scenarios.",
    "persona_show_hints": "Kwerekana ubufashaful impanuro kuri bigira hamwe na persona. impanuro shiramwo historically relevant ikibazo ku ask, topics umuntu would find interesting, na amabwiriza ico lead ku deeper understanding. Gikomeye kuri umunyeshure who need scaffolding canke aren't sure how ku begin historical interview.",
    "persona_submit_btn": "Rungika cawe ubutumwa ku persona umuntu. cawe ikibazo canke response ni analyzed kuri relevance na ubujambere. AI persona will respond authentically bishingiye kuri their historical context, knowledge, na personality. Well-crafted ikibazo ico erekana historical understanding earn bonus XP.",
    "persona_close": "Yugara persona conversation urubaho. cawe ibiganiro history na earned XP ni automatically vyabitswe. wewe can resume iki conversation later kuva History tab.",
    "persona_close_title": "Yugara Persona ibiganiro",
    "persona_reflection_input": "Andika cawe igitekerezo kuri conversation kuri igenzura. Reflect kuri iki wewe learned ku byerekeye historical figure, how their perspective differs kuva uburyorn viewpoints, na how iki conversation changed cawe understanding. Reflections ni evaluated gukoresha rubric aligned ku historical thinking ubuhinga na can earn significant XP.",
    "persona_conclude": "End conversation na kora comprehensive incamake ca cawe discussion. incamake hariho: key topics covered, historical insights gained, quality ca cawe ikibazo, empathy demonstrated, na XP earned. Iki incamake can be exported kuri igenzura, added ku umunyeshure portfolios, canke vyakoreshejwe as kwandika prompt kuri igitekerezo activities.",
    "persona_save_chat": "Bika iki conversation ku gusubiramwo canke sangira later. Bikad chats preserve uzuza dialogue, XP earned, timestamps, na any igitekerezos. Koresha vyabitswe chats kuri umunyeshure portfolios, igenzura ibimenyetso, ishuri discussions, canke exemplar uburyols. Bikad conversations can be exported as PDF canke shared hamwe na ikindi umunyeshure.",
    "persona_topic_spark": "Get conversation starter canke ikiyago suggestion igihe wewe're ntibi sure iki ku ask. sisitemu irakora historically relevant ikibazo bishingiye kuri persona's background, expertise, na time period. Gikomeye kuri overcoming writer's block canke discovering gisha aho bihurira ku sesengura muri cawe historical inquiry.",
    "persona_auto_send": "Automatically rungika cawe ubutumwa igihe wewe hagarika typing kuri few amasegonda. Creates vyinshi natural conversational flow, especially igihe gukoresha ijwi dictation. Hagarika iki niba wewe prefer ku gusubiramwo na hindura ubutumwa before sending, canke niba wewe need vyinshi time ku compose thoughtful responses.",
    "analysis_generate_button": "Sesengura cawe imvo inyandiko kuri reading urwego, ingorane, na ibiranga.",
    "analysis_check_accuracy": "Fact-check imvo ibirimwo against reliable references.",
    "outline_generate_button": "Kora ibibonwa organizer kuva cawe imvo ibirimwo.",
    "timeline_generate_button": "Kora timeline ca events kuva cawe imvo ibirimwo.",
    "timeline_topic": "main ikiyago canke icigwa ca timeline being vyakozwe. AI irema historically accurate events bishingiye kuri iki ikiyago na cawe imvo ibirimwo. akarorero topics: American Revolution, Life Cycle ca Stars, Shakespeare's Career. Events ni automatically ordered chronologically kuri sequencing kora imyitozo.",
    "timeline_count": "umubare ca events ku shiramwo muri timeline. vyinshi events rema longer, vyinshi birimo ibisigura timelines ariko increase ingorane. Recommended: 4-6 events kuri beginners, 8-10 kuri intermediate, 12+ kuri co hejuru abanyeshuri. Events ni draggable kuri sequencing kora imyitozo after igisekuru.",
    "faq_custom_instructions": "Ongerako kanaka requirements kuri FAQ ikibazo (e.g., 'Focus kuri misconceptions').",
    "faq_count": "umubare ca FAQ ikibazo-inyishu pairs ku kora.",
