    "roster_panel_header": "ishuri Roster Key ni cawe differentiation command center. Rema umunyeshure umugwis hamwe na unique kwiga profiles (urwego rw'ishuri, ururimi, reading urwego, interests, DOK), then apply those profiles ku any generator. Roster amakuru ni stored muri cawe browser's local storage na never leaves cawe device unless wewe explicitly rungika hanze canke sync ku mu buryo butaziguye igihe. Koresha 'Shirira mu ngiro ku Generator' ku instantly configure ihirahirwa kuri umugwi, canke 'Differentiate by Group' ku batch-kora umutungo kuri vyose umugwis at once.",
    "roster_import_export": "Zana imbere previously exported roster JSON dosiye, canke rungika hanze cawe current roster kuri backup canke sharing hagati devices. Exported dosiye contain umugwi names, ibara, umunyeshure assignments, na vyose profile ihirahirwa.",
    "roster_sync_session": "Push cawe roster umugwi metadata ku gikora Firebase igihe so umunyeshure ni automatically assigned ku their designated umugwi igihe they join. Group-kanaka ihirahirwa (TTS umuvuduko, karaoke uburyo) take effect kuri umunyeshure devices.",
    "roster_batch_generate": "Kora differentiated umutungo kuri every umugwi simultaneously. Hitamwo which umutungo types ku rema (adapted inyandiko, inkoranya, ikizamini, etc.) na sisitemu will iterate biciye buri umugwi, applying their profile ihirahirwa before kurema. umutungo ni tagged hamwe na umugwi identifiers kuri vyoroshe filtering.",
    "bridge_send_button": "Yugurura Bridge uburyo ku rungika indimi zibiri ubutumwa ku umunyeshure during mu buryo butaziguye amategeko. Type igitekerezo, umurongo w'amajambo, canke amategeko, hitamwo uburyo (Explain, Translate, canke ibibonwa+Explain), na hitamwo intumbero umugwi. ubutumwa ni vyakozwe gukoresha AI hamwe na umugwi's ururimi na reading urwego ihirahirwa, then displayed as large, readable indimi zibiri urubaho kuri umunyeshure devices hamwe na TTS na karaoke highlighting.",
